# Web3 Payment App – Circle Wallet Setup & Auth State

This project is part of the **Building a Web3 Payment App (Fullstack Series)** where we build a real-world payment application step by step using modern Web3 tools and infrastructure.

In this part of the series, we integrate **Circle Developer-Controlled Wallets**, manage authentication state using **Zustand**, and connect authenticated users to wallet infrastructure.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Web3 Authentication using Privy
- Circle Developer-Controlled Wallets
- Wallet Set Creation
- Wallet Creation (Base Sepolia)
- Zustand Auth State Management
- Backend Token Verification
- User Wallet Linking

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React
- Zustand
- Privy Auth

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express
- Circle SDK

### Blockchain
- Base Sepolia

